      <title>Seven & I 的提案推动了日本零售商如永旺的崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/seven-i-proposal-fuels-rally-in-japanese-retailers-like-aeon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 的收购提案引发了投资者对永旺株式会社 (Aeon Co.) 等其他日本零售商的兴趣，从而推高了这些公司的股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/seven-i-proposal-fuels-rally-in-japanese-retailers-like-aeon</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 01:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：交易员考虑美联储降息幅度 美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的美国数据让投资者对美联储下周预期降息幅度产生猜测，导致美国国债价格上涨，美元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
